msgstr "Zoiper Lite"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/voip/devices_integrations.rst:96
msgid ""
"*Zoiper Lite* is a free :abbr:`VoIP (Voice over Internet Protocol)` "
":abbr:`SIP (Session Initiation Protocol)` dialer with voice and video."
